description: A walk around Brook Green with emphasis on the buried lost river, Stamford Brook.

factsheet.heading: Brook Green
paragraphs: A walk to follow the course of one of London's lost rivers, Stamford Brook. There are three tributaries in West London. The one which runs under Brook Green was used extensively for various industrial processes, and we will explore some of the reminders of these uses

location.address: Hammersmith station, Hammersmith and City line, W6 7AA

name: Brook Green walk
